tooltips_plus_onboarding.outro.descripti.string: Frames, text, and the design panel: With these basics down, you’re ready for your first project.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.no_nav_frames_d.string: Click and drag a blank spot on the canvas to draw a frame. Frames are containers for your designs that you can also use to draw UI elements.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.change_properti.string: Change properties in the design panel

tooltips_plus_onboarding.next_take_some_.string: Next take some time to adjust your frame’s size, corner radius, fill—whatever you like.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.go_to_a_blank_s.string: Go to a blank spot in your canvas

tooltips_plus_onboarding.hold_right_clic.string: Hold right click while moving your mouse.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.hold_space_and_.string: Hold {spaceKey} and left click while moving your mouse.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.swipe_your_trac.string: Swipe your trackpad with two fingers

tooltips_plus_onboarding.presets_ending_.string: Templates are always here for you
If you’d like to save time or are feeling stuck, add pre-made UI whenever you like.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.assets_ending_s.string: Assets are always here for you
Quickly find components whenever you need them by opening the {strongAssets} tab.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.ui_kits_ending_.string: UI kits are always here for you
If you’d like to save time or are feeling stuck, add pre-made UI whenever you like.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.text_step.title.string: Add text layers with your toolbar

tooltips_plus_onboarding.text_step.descr.string: Click into your frame, and start typing to create a text layer.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.presets_step.de.string: Use a template to jump start your designs, then make it your own.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.assets_step.des.string: Use components from a team library or a UI kit provided by Figma to jump-start your design—then make them your own.

tooltips_plus_onboarding.ui_kits_step.de.string: Use UI kits from Apple, Google, or Figma to jump-start your designs, then make them your own.

universal_insert.saved_for_quick_access_.string: Save for quicker access to your favorite widgets
